      <title>马士基退出竞购物流巨头德铁信克</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/maersk-is-said-to-consider-dropping-out-of-db-schenker-bidding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[A.P. 穆勒-马士基集团撤回了对德国铁路股份公司 (Deutsche Bahn AG) 物流部门 DB Schenker 的收购要约，据报道，该部门的估值超过 150 亿欧元（161 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/maersk-is-said-to-consider-dropping-out-of-db-schenker-bidding</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 10:15:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>撼动拉丁美洲的对冲基金巨头在墨西哥暴露无遗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/hedge-fund-whales-rocking-latin-america-are-exposed-in-mexico</link>
      <description><![CDATA[6 月 7 日清晨，墨西哥利率期货大幅上涨。整整一周，尽管墨西哥执政党左翼党在选举中取得压倒性胜利，比索大幅下跌，但利率期货一直保持稳定。但现在，抛售突然蔓延到了利率市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/hedge-fund-whales-rocking-latin-america-are-exposed-in-mexico</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
